    "description": "Go on a quest to obtain a hotdog!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nExplore over seven realms in search of the elusive cylindrical meats, from the heights of Mustard Mountain to the ominous caverns of the Underdark.<br />\r\nIn the course of your journey you will uncover secrets both hilarious and unnerving, as well as a plethora of inscrutable video game references.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAcross the many realms you will encounter friendly NPCs and challenging platforming.  <br />\r\nNPCs have small side-quests for you to complete within their realm, such as finding a cowboy's lost cow or helping to harvest grapes in a vineyard.<br />\r\nHelp people with their problems and they will help you back, whether it is with information, powerups or coins.<br />\r\nCoins can also be collected in the world, encouraging exploration off the main path and giving a helping hand if you can't figure out the way to go.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs well as running and jumping, you're also able to drive vehicles such as cars and planes to reach areas you wouldn't be able to on foot!<br />\r\nPlay with powerups such as double jump, dash, and glide.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game is highly stylised, with a low-res low-framerate look and a reduced color palette. Adding to this is a retro soundtrack and bit crushed dialogue audio.<br />\r\nThis stylisation can be turned off in the settings, and NPC dialogue is shown in a subtitle box at the bottom of the screen.",
